parameters:
Underling: Aaaaah, Lord Shark has been defeated... It's
impossible after all... There's no monster that can beat
Dynamite Abalone!!

Dynamite Abalone: Wabi wabi... Once I take this one down,
all that's left are the monsters with damaged suits who
can't fight, those who've retired... and the rest are just
underling small fry! The fun times are about to begin...

Bunny-chan: Gyah-!? Something's coming this way! Stop... Go
away-!

Memimi: Bunny-chan's monster suit is specially made, with a
stun gun built into it! It's dangerous when monsters get too
excited during Monster Fight...

Dynamite Abalone: Damn it, that pisses me off... If it
weren't for my abalone armor, that would have been
dangerous... Reporting to the mayor can wait, I'm going to
make you pay!!
Bunny-chan: Eek, it's not very effective... Kyah-!!?

Memimi: Aaaaah, Bunny-chan is ah...! Grr, everyone's taken
damage... I still can't move...
